description: Flaky fish fillets with a stunning balance of Moroccan spices and veggie-filled couscous. You won't believe how easy it is to make this delicious dinner.
keywords: Pan-Fried Moroccan-Style Fish With Veggie Couscous
name: Pan-Fried Moroccan-Style Fish With Veggie Couscous Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat remaining oil in same cleaned pan over medium-high heat. Cook fish for 2 minutes on each side or until golden and cooked through. Serve fish over couscous with rocket and extra lemon cheeks.
